================================================================================
NOTE ON COMPONENT LICENSES
================================================================================

bindsight itself is MIT-licensed. However, bindsight orchestrates external
tools and data sources whose licenses differ. See LICENSING.md for the full
inventory and per-tool commercial-use guidance. In particular:

  - AlphaFold2 weights (when used via the optional AF2-IG validator path)
    are released by DeepMind under terms restricting commercial use.
  - DESeq2 / edgeR (the optional R-bridge DEG path) are GPL-licensed.

These are runtime dependencies and are NOT vendored in this repository. The
default bindsight paths use only MIT/Apache/BSD/CC-BY components.
